                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for improving specific resistance of composite semicoke reducing agent for industrial silicon",
                    "一种提高工业硅用复合半焦还原剂比电阻的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a method for improving the specific resistance of a composite semicoke reducing agent for industrial silicon, and belongs to the technical field of composite reducing agents for industrial silicon. The method comprises the following steps: respectively crushing and grinding vacuum-dried bituminous coal and vacuum-dried petroleum coke until the particle size is 3-8cm to obtain microspherical bituminous coal particles and microspherical petroleum coke particles, uniformly mixing the microspherical bituminous coal particles and the microspherical petroleum coke particles to obtain a microspherical mixture, adding water into the microspherical mixture, and mixing and grinding to obtain a mixture A; adding a silicon slag modifier into the mixture A, and uniformly grinding to obtain a mixture B; carrying out microwave carbonization modification on the mixture B in a protective gas atmosphere, and cooling to room temperature to obtain a modified mixture C; and placing the modified mixture C in a protective gas atmosphere, introducing an activating agent hydrogen, activating for 45-90 minutes at the temperature of 550-850 DEG C, and cooling to room temperature to obtain the high-specific-resistance composite semicoke reducing agent for industrial silicon. The composite semicoke reducing agent is high in fixed carbon content, low in price, high in specific resistance, good in reaction activity and good in compressive strength."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种提高工业硅用复合半焦还原剂比电阻的方法，属于工业硅用复合还原剂技术领域。本发明将真空干燥的烟煤和真空干燥的石油焦分别破碎研磨至粒度为3～8cm得到微球状烟煤颗粒和微球状石油焦颗粒，微球状烟煤颗粒和微球状石油焦颗粒混合均匀得到微球状混合物，将水加入到微球状混合物中混合研磨得到混料A；将硅渣改性剂加入到混料A中进行研磨均匀得到混料B；将混料B置于保护气氛围下微波碳化改性，冷却至室温得到改性混合料C；改性混合料C置于保护气氛围下并通入活化剂氢气，在温度550～850℃下活化45～90min，冷却至室温得到高比电阻的工业硅用复合半焦还原剂。本发明复合半焦还原剂固定碳含量高、价格低廉、比电阻高、反应活性好、抗压强度好。"
                }
            ]
